title: Starliner Flight Day 3 Activities
summary: Starliner and Expedition crews work together to conduct flight test objectives and evaluate spacecraft capabilities. NASA astronauts Butch Wilmore and Suni Williams continue to settle into the pace of the International Space Station (ISS) after flying Boeing’s Starliner spacecraft, named Calypso, to the orbital complex.
